original_title: N'effacez pas nos traces ! Dominique Grange, une chanteuse engagée
overview: Songs of Dominique Grange carry the spirit of May 1968 riots. Committed singer, she has marked her era and became an icon. Nowadays, she is still engaged against oppression in every shape and form.
title: N'effacez pas nos traces ! Dominique Grange, une chanteuse engagée
